  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个Git流程图，展示三个分支的结构，而且每个分支都要有一次cherry-pick操作。整体布局用从上到下的方式（TB），这样阅读起来比较直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gitGraph TB",
        "branch",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，TB布局。那三个分支具体是哪些？main作为主干，另外两个是develop和featureA吗？还有cherry-pick是从每个分支各挑一次提交吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "featureA",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，main、develop、featureA三个分支。cherry-pick的场景是：从develop挑一个提交到main，再从featureA挑一个提交到main。develop最后还要合并featureA。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "featureA",
        "cherry-pick",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先搭建骨架。main起点叫\"ZERO\"，然后分出develop，develop上先做一个提交\"A\"。回到main再做\"ONE\"，这样两条线就并行起来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ZERO",
        "develop",
        "A",
        "ONE",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "develop上继续，在\"A\"之后再加一个\"B\"，然后从\"B\"的位置分出featureA分支。featureA上要有两次修复提交，叫\"FIX\"和\"FIX-2\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "B",
        "featureA",
        "FIX",
        "FIX-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在main这边做到\"TWO\"了，接下来做第一次cherry-pick——把develop上的\"A\"挑过来，然后main继续到\"THREE\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "TWO",
        "cherry-pick",
        "A",
        "THREE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "第二次cherry-pick是在\"THREE\"之后吧？把featureA上的\"FIX\"挑到main。注意是\"FIX\"不是\"FIX-2\"，我们只挑第一次修复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "THREE",
        "cherry-pick",
        "FIX",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我确认一下——之前我差点写成挑\"FIX-2\"，现在修正为挑\"FIX\"。然后develop这边最后要checkout回去，加一个\"C\"，再执行merge featureA，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIX",
        "develop",
        "C",
        "merge",
        "featureA"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。最后给整个图加个标题吧：\"Three branches and a cherry-pick from each (top-to-bottom)\"，这样一眼就能看出核心内容。",
